Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}どうしよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}大暴走獰猛な鼓動を
